headline: Stock Futures Rise as Risk Rebound Builds Steam
summary: Stock futures were rising on Wednesday, as investors carried on snapping up Bitcoin and other risk-on assets following a recent wobble. Earnings from retailers Macy’s and Dollar Tree could give investors a sense of how consumer spending is holding up.

headline: ADP reports decline of 32,000 private sector jobs in November
summary: ADP reported a monthly decline of 32,000 US private sector jobs in November, coming well below economists' forecasts of a gain of 40,000 private payrolls.
